      <title>民主党赢得威斯康星州倾向共和党的沃克夏市长竞选。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/waukesha-wisconsin-mayoral-race-result.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该市共同委员会主席艾丽西亚·哈尔文斯莱本 (Alicia Halvensleben) 击败了一名共和党议员，延续了特朗普时代民主党在市长职位上的一系列胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/waukesha-wisconsin-mayoral-race-result.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 03:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
