    <item>
      <title>在佐治亚州第 14 区特别决选中，民主党实现了迄今为止最大的转变</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/elections/georgia-house-special-shifts.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肖恩·哈里斯在第 14 国会选区落后了约 12 个百分点，但他将该选区向左移动了 25 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/elections/georgia-house-special-shifts.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 02:44:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>停火消息传出前几小时，教皇利奥十四世对特朗普发出强烈谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/middleeast/pope-leo-xiv-trump-iran-threats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位出生于美国的第一位教皇一直呼吁通过对话解决中东战争。他称特朗普的伊朗威胁“确实不可接受”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/world/middleeast/pope-leo-xiv-trump-iran-threats.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 02:04:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自由派法官克里斯·泰勒赢得威斯康星州最高法院竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/wisconsin-supreme-court-election-result.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着克里斯·泰勒法官的胜利，自由派增加了对法院的控制。威斯康星州最高法院的竞选经常引起全国关注，但今年不会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/us/wisconsin-supreme-court-election-result.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 01:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
